I have hacked the cartridge version of Bio Miracle to MMC5. I also have looked into hacking some mapper 90 games like SMW and Final Fight 3. However, they are programmed so wonky, Final Fight 3 for instance is designed apparently with traps to discourage modification of the game causing crashes when you modify certain parts. I lost interest in trying to hack mapper 90 games when I ran up against that resistance as I have little interest putting alot of effort into hacking a really shitty game. Sorry, but SMW sucks, FF3 sucks, it's just a novelty and one I certainly can do without.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=1726">MottZilla</a> — Sun Oct 04, 2009 10:47 am</p><hr />
